1. Pokušajte da završite ovaj zadatak do kraja dana. (*Pokušajte*) (Try to finish this task by the end of the day.) 
2. Ja sam već *pokušao* da popravim ovaj automobil, ali nisam uspeo. (I have already tried to fix this car, but I failed.) 
3. Ako *pokušate* da uđete u ovu sobu, moraćete da otključate vrata. (If you try to enter this room, you will need to unlock the door.)
4. *Pokušajte* da se opustite i ne brinite previše. (Try to relax and don't worry too much.)
5. Nije dovoljno samo *pokušati*, morate da date sve od sebe. (It's not enough to just try, you have to give it your all.)
6. Koliko puta ste *pokušali* da razgovarate sa svojim šefom o ovom problemu? (How many times have you tried to talk to your boss about this issue?)
7. Možete da *pokušate* da rešite ovaj test, ali nećete imati mnogo vremena. (You can try to solve this test, but you won't have much time.)
8. Da li ste *pokušali* da pozovete svog prijatelja na telefon? (Have you tried to call your friend on the phone?)
9. Ne *pokušavajte* da me ubedite u nešto u šta ne verujem. (Don't try to convince me of something I don't believe in.)
10. *Pokušajte* da se setite kada ste poslednji put bili ovde. (Try to remember when was the last time you were here.)